@startuml
title 🏋️ Cas d'usage 1 : Lancer une séance d'entraînement 💪

actor "👤 Utilisateur" as User
participant "🖥️ Front-End\n(React)" as Frontend
participant "⚙️ Back-End\n(FastAPI)" as Backend
participant "🗄️ Database\n(PostgreSQL)" as Database

User -> Frontend: 🤩 Clique "Let's go ! Démarre ta séance"
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Backend: 📡 GET /api/workouts/1
activate Backend
note right of Backend: Récupération des infos\nde la séance

Backend -> Database: 🔍 SELECT workout WHERE id=1
activate Database
Database --> Backend: ✅ Workout data
deactivate Database

Backend -> Database: 🔍 SELECT exercises\nFROM workout_exercises\nWHERE workout_id=1
activate Database
Database --> Backend:  Liste des exercices\n(Pompes, Squats, Planche...)
deactivate Database

Backend --> Frontend: 🎯💪 JSON {workout, exercises[]}
deactivate Backend
note left of Frontend: Préparation de\nl'affichage

Frontend --> User: 🥵🎊 Affiche ta séance :\n"3 exercices te attendent !"
deactivate Frontend

@enduml